      content: "(\u3063 \u0361 \u0361\xBA - \u0361 \u0361\xBA \u03C2)"
      isOldConversation: 0
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Leo
      content: "Adic\u0103\u2026 cum naiba se mut\u0103 pointerele alea? C\u0103
        am impresia c\u0103 profesorul vorbea klingonian\u0103."
      isOldConversation: 0
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Rina
      content: "G\xE2nde\u0219te-te la o instala\u021Bie de art\u0103 dintr-un coridor
        lung."
      isOldConversation: 0
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Rina
      content: "Pe fiecare perete sunt ag\u0103\u021Bate sculpturi, \u0219i \xEEntre
        ele exist\u0103 fire vizibile care le conecteaz\u0103 \u2014 unul spre sculptura
        anterioar\u0103, altul spre urm\u0103toarea."
      isOldConversation: 0
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Rina
      content: "Dac\u0103 vrei s\u0103 adaugi o sculptur\u0103 nou\u0103 \xEEntre
        dou\u0103 existente, trebuie s\u0103 mu\u021Bi firele \u2014 s\u0103 tai
        leg\u0103tura dintre cele dou\u0103 vechi \u0219i s\u0103 legi noua pies\u0103
        la ambele."
      isOldConversation: 0
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Rina
      content: "Asta e o list\u0103 dublu \xEEnl\u0103n\u021Buit\u0103: fiecare element
        \u201E\u0219tie\u201D de cine a fost \xEEnainte \u0219i de cine vine dup\u0103."
      isOldConversation: 0
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Rina
      content: "A\u0219a po\u021Bi merge \xEEn ambele direc\u021Bii prin \u201Eexpozi\u021Bie\u201D
        \u2014 \xEEnainte \u0219i \xEEnapoi \u2014 f\u0103r\u0103 s\u0103 pierzi
        vreun fir."
      isOldConversation: 0
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Leo
      content: "Ooohh damn, ok, acum chiar vizualizez.\nDeci dac\u0103 \u201Etai
        firele\u201D f\u0103r\u0103 grij\u0103, se pr\u0103bu\u0219e\u0219te expozi\u021Bia."
      isOldConversation: 0
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Rina
      content: "Exact. De asta e nevoie s\u0103 actualizezi leg\u0103turile, nu doar
        s\u0103 adaugi sculptura."
      isOldConversation: 0
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Leo
      content: "wow. de ce explic\u0103 nimeni lucrurile a\u0219a? e\u0219ti o legend\u0103"
      isOldConversation: 0
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Leo
      content: "te scot la un ceai drept mul\u021Bumire?"
      isOldConversation: 0
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Rina
      content: ai zis ceai, da? nu vin.
      isOldConversation: 0
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Rina
      content: mai vedem
      isOldConversation: 0
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
  - contactName: Illuminati
    messages:
    - sender: Illuminati
      content: Te vedem
      isOldConversation: 1
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Rina
      content: Nu imi pasaaaaaa!!!!!!!!!!!!
      isOldConversation: 1
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Illuminati
      content: E nu
      isOldConversation: 1
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Illuminati
      content: Hai ca nu daca e
      isOldConversation: 1
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Illuminati
      content: JOEVERRRR
      isOldConversation: 1
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Illuminati
      content: esti joever
      isOldConversation: 1
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Rina
      content: nu tu
      isOldConversation: 1
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
  - contactName: Fostu
    messages:
    - sender: Fostu
      content: "\xCEmi pare a\u0219a de r\u0103u pentru tot."
      isOldConversation: 1
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Fostu
      content: "Dac\u0103 a\u0219 putea da timpul \xEEnapoi, a\u0219 face-o."
      isOldConversation: 1
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Fostu
      content: "Dar nu pot. \u0218i nu \u0219tiu cum a\u0219 putea s\u0103 te rec\xE2\u0219tig."
      isOldConversation: 1
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Fostu
      content: "Meri\u021Bi pe cineva mult mai bun dec\xE2t mine..."
      isOldConversation: 1
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Fostu
      content: "M\u0103 tot uit la tabloul \u0103la cu frunza albastr\u0103\u2026"
      isOldConversation: 1
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Fostu
      content: "\xCEnc\u0103 miroase a tine. Sau poate doar mi se pare."
      isOldConversation: 1
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Fostu
      content: "Ai fost la expozi\u021Bie? Am v\u0103zut ni\u0219te story-uri."
      isOldConversation: 1
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Fostu
      content: "P\u0103reai obosit\u0103\u2026"
      isOldConversation: 1
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Fostu
      content: "Rina\u2026\n\xCEmi lipsesc p\xE2n\u0103 \u0219i certurile cu tine.\nE\u0219ti
        singura persoan\u0103 care m-a v\u0103zut cu adev\u0103rat.\nF\u0103r\u0103
        tine e doar lini\u0219te. \u0218i lini\u0219tea asta m\u0103 sf\xE2\u0219ie."
      isOldConversation: 1
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
    - sender: Fostu
      content: "Dac\u0103 ai citi m\u0103car unul din mesajele astea, te rog... scrie-mi
        \u201Enu\u201D. At\xE2t. S\u0103 \u0219tiu c\u0103 nu mai e nicio \u0219ans\u0103."
      isOldConversation: 1
      hasChoices: 0
      responseOptions: []
